Bondi Partners is an advisory firm offering strategic counsel in a rapidly-evolving world. With teams in Washington and Sydney, we work together to cover North America and Australia. Our team provides discreet counsel, impactful partnerships and tailored solutions.

Learn more: bondipartners.com
